# 10. Deployment Plan

The project will be deployed using cloud hosting services.

## Frontend Deployment

* Build the React application.
* Deploy using **Vercel**.
* Configure production environment variables.

---

## Backend Deployment

* Deploy the Express.js server using **Render**.
* Configure environment variables:

  * MongoDB URI
  * JWT Secret
  * Client URL
  * Port Number

---

## Database Deployment

* Host the database using **MongoDB Atlas**.
* Configure database users and network access.
* Connect the backend API securely.

---

## Environment Variables

### Frontend

```env
VITE_API_URL=https://your-backend-url
```

### Backend

```env
PORT=5000
MONGODB_URI=your_mongodb_connection_string
JWT_SECRET=your_secure_secret_key
CLIENT_URL=https://your-frontend-url
```

---

